<keyLead pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<number box="[151,165,1662,1683]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" value="9.0">9</number>
. Longer haired species, longest ocellar hairs longer than narrowest width of frons, third antennal segment about 
<date box="[1305,1329,1662,1683]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<number box="[1305,1317,1662,1683]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" value="2.0">2</number>
