, r-m and m-cu crossveins, 
<number box="[1001,1010,1692,1713]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" value="1.0">1</number>
st basal cell clear subapically, 
<number box="[1303,1314,1692,1713]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" value="2.0">2</number>
nd basal cell largely clear (
<figureCitation box="[359,444,1723,1744]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="9.[151,250,869,891]" captionText="FIGURE 3. ♂ U. aenea wing of long-haired form." pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
