</caption>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,929,1043]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
<keyLead pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
- Shorter haired species, longest ocellar hairs shorter than narrowest width of frons, third antennal segment about 
<number box="[1289,1318,929,950]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" value="1.5">1.5</number>
x scape plus pedicel, infuscation of wing filling 
<number box="[564,576,961,982]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" value="1.0">1</number>
st and 
<number box="[631,643,961,982]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" value="2.0">2</number>
nd basal cell so without isolated darker spots over origin of R 
